Comment: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:27.99,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Ohana...
Comment: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:32.37,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Ohana, if you did it, believing that was the best idea,
Comment: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll definitely work out!
