Comment: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:38.04,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Ko...
Comment: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.58,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Comment: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:43.84,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,You're right, things will work out somehow!
Comment: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:45.38,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Thanks, Ko!
Comment: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:48.47,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay... I'm glad I was able to be of some use. {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:49.72,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,You're awesome!
Comment: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.72,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,You're awesome, Ko!
