Comment: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:23.03,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Hello, you've reached Kissui Inn.
Comment: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:25.87,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Order a massage for the customers in the Moon Room.
Comment: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:27.37,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Right now!
Comment: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.00,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Time is money!
Comment: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:32.83,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,And I'll need you to take care of the\N customers in the Wave Room during dinner.
Comment: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.63,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,
Comment: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:37.75,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\i1}Roger! I, Jiromaru, will demonstrate my best work! {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,we are unfortunately fully booked tonight.
Comment: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.84,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Oh...
Comment: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:41.51,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,No, it's fine.
Comment: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:43.01,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Comment: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:49.39,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,What {\i1}am{\i0} I doing?
Comment: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:51.69,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you wait.
Comment: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:54.86,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,A helmet?
Comment: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:58.19,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,The staff at the parking lot lent me one.
Comment: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:05.57,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Uh... Sorry, I figured everything\N would go well if I were to bring you back.
Comment: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:10.70,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,You were supposed to be\N enjoying your friend's wedding too.
Comment: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for...
Comment: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:18.84,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,You came here thinking this would be for the best, right?
Comment: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.09,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.30,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Then I'm fine with it.
Comment: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.76,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,If you trusted me enough to\N think that I'd make everything work,
Comment: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to do just that.
Comment: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:34.02,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
