Comment: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:54.50,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Comment: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:56.75,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Hang on tight!
Comment: 0,0:12:57.75,0:12:59.38,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Umm...
Comment: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.26,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Pardon me!
Comment: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:32.41,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inside this oversized helmet\N was a scent unfamiliar to me.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:38.33,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is what a boy's hair smells like?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:40.67,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ko's hair, too?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Comment: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:13.08,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,According to Minchi, Mr. Ren is a bit...
Comment: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,different today.
Comment: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:16.29,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.92,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Miyagishi Tohru, reporting for duty!
Comment: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:27.22,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,I apologize for being late!
Comment: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:34.60,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Mr. Ren.
Comment: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:37.64,Default,Renji,0,0,0,,Right. Get to work right away.
Comment: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:39.23,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Comment: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:54.37,Default,Min,0,0,0,,How did you find him?
Comment: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.75,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to Ko.
Comment: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:57.87,Default,Min,0,0,0,,Who?
Comment: 0,0:14:57.87,0:14:59.87,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,It's a long story.
Comment: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:00.87,Default,Min,0,0,0,,Then whatever.
Comment: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:04.92,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Isn't that where you're supposed to say, "Doesn't matter. Tell me"?
Comment: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.88,Default,Min,0,0,0,,Get to your workstation already.
Comment: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:10.26,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Do you mind letting Minko do the frying, Mr. Ren?
Comment: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:10.80,Default,Renji,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Comment: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:12.51,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Minko!
Comment: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:13.76,Default,Min,0,0,0,,Okay!
Comment: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:16.60,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Fry up the tempura.
Comment: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:17.31,Default,Min,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:18.77,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,What, you can't even do that?
Comment: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.10,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,What have you been watching all this time?
Comment: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:22.65,Default,Min,0,0,0,,Right! I mean...
Comment: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:23.73,Default,Min,0,0,0,,Yes, I can do it!
Comment: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:26.86,Default,Min,0,0,0,,I'll do it! Please let me!
Comment: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:28.61,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Okay!
Comment: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:44.88,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I felt like I heard the noise of\N something starting to operate.
Comment: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:48.38,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,I see.
Comment: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:49.76,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Is that notebook helping out?
Comment: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.38,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Comment: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:53.26,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Madam Manager really is amazing.
Comment: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:54.59,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Comment: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:57.56,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Well, I do keep a notebook of my own, too.
Comment: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:58.85,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Really?
Comment: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:02.52,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,What? Stop acting so surprised.
Comment: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:04.77,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Okay, let's get to work!
Comment: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.57,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Umm, Tomoe...
Comment: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Comment: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:13.20,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,All customers are equal, thus,\N we need to treat them all equally.
Comment: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.70,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,That's what Madam Manager lives for!
Comment: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.45,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,That's what Kissui Inn stands for!
Comment: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:18.16,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Right?
Comment: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:20.37,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Comment: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:43.73,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,I made a mistake.
Comment: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:55.91,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,There.
Comment: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:05.58,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,This is our inn's special meal.
Comment: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.92,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Special bamboo.
Comment: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:15.84,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Please enjoy!
Comment: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:19.01,Default,Old,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Comment: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.23,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Comment: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.94,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Please enjoy your stay.
Comment: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:27.77,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,This is so good!
Comment: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.73,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,We're done over here, Mr. Ren!
Comment: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:32.03,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,Okay. Now I need you to do the kneading.
Comment: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:32.94,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Comment: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:39.78,Default,Min,0,0,0,,Six... Seven... Eight...
Comment: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.45,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,The sound has changed!
Comment: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:42.16,Default,Min,0,0,0,,Right!
Comment: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:46.62,Default,Min,0,0,0,,Do you mind tasting my fish tempura?
Comment: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:47.46,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Sure!
Comment: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:53.55,Default,Min,0,0,0,,Here.
Comment: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:00.35,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,It's good. Go with this.
Comment: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.47,Default,Min,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Comment: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:04.02,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Did you note how the oil\N sound changed when it was ready?
Comment: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:04.85,Default,Min,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Comment: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.48,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Oh, you were here.
Comment: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:08.85,Default,Min,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing?!
Comment: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:11.86,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I was feeling warm and delighted.
Comment: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:13.65,Default,Min,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Comment: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:14.94,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Warm, huh...
Comment: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:18.61,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Well, for her first time, it was indeed well-done.
Comment: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:20.82,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I wasn't talking about the taste of the tempura.
Comment: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:22.91,Default,Min,0,0,0,,So, what do you want?
Comment: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:25.04,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I came to grab the tempura.
Comment: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:25.91,Default,Min,0,0,0,,Give me a second.
Comment: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be done soon.
Comment: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:35.26,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you enjoying your night?
Comment: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:36.76,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Comment: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:41.43,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're enjoying yourself?
Comment: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:48.18,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's the spot...
Comment: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:01.07,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Good night!
Comment: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:03.12,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Good night!
Comment: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.12,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Comment: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:04.91,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,See you!
Comment: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:11.88,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,And this is how we were able to get\N through a long day without Madam Manager.
Comment: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:29.52,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Ohana, the customers in the Moon Room are leaving.
Comment: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.64,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Okay!
Comment: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.77,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything.
Comment: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:38.11,Default,All,0,0,0,,We'll be awaiting your return!
Comment: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:45.45,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,We're bound to score high if those customers are the mystery guests!
Comment: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.49,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter who the mystery guests were.
Comment: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:50.16,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,We gave our all to every customer, after all.
Comment: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:52.67,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Yes, but scores are important.
Comment: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:53.63,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Comment: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:56.92,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Okay, Ohana, you've still got some work left.
Comment: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:58.00,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Okay!
