Comment: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:34.08,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Nah, it's fine now.
Comment: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:38.50,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You had a good time, right, Mom?
Comment: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:42.13,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was able to rest so well!
Comment: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.68,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
