Comment: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:47.68,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Let's.
Comment: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:48.51,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Oh.
Comment: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:51.31,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Let me help.
Comment: 0,0:20:51.73,0:20:53.06,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Comment: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:58.44,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Ko, it didn't matter who the mystery guests were.
Comment: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:01.44,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,We treat every customer equally.
Comment: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:03.70,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Hey, Ko?
Comment: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:07.03,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,It was thanks to you that I was able to work so hard.
Comment: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:08.87,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Comment: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:17.79,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Koichi?
Comment: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:19.59,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Yes?
Comment: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:22.38,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,The new item that came in yesterday...
Comment: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.38,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,I'll bring it right away!
Comment: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:26.30,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Comment: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:27.89,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Comment: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:30.85,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,As soon as she saw my face, she almost fainted.
Comment: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:33.02,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Imagine how I felt.
Comment: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:36.81,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,That's mean. I was desperate.
Comment: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:40.32,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,This is good!
Comment: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:43.07,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know!
Comment: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:45.11,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Guys, she's back.
Comment: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:52.95,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Comment: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:05.01,Default,All,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Madam Manager!
Comment: 0,0:22:06.09,0:22:07.63,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Glad to be back.
Comment: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:34.18,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,No, that's not it, Ohana!
Comment: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:35.39,Default,Min,0,0,0,,You can't do everything by yourself.
Comment: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:37.27,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Come home, Ohana.
