Dialogue: 100,0:21:16.38,0:21:17.80,Dialogue,Sen,0,0,0,,{}Koichi-kun?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:18.47,0:21:19.47,Dialogue,Ko,0,0,0,,{}Vâng?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:19.47,0:21:22.39,Dialogue,Sen,0,0,0,,{}Món hàng mới đến hôm qua...
